From Chris:
I would say the raffinose_vs_wt would be a good exemplar.
Raffinose = wild type cells starved for glucose but supplemented with raffinose for 6 hours.
wt = wild type cells grown in glucose
There will be massive shifts in expression, with pathways truly turned on/off, stress response triggered, etc etc.


